[Developer Options & Sample Viewer (in-game)]
author=Hacc
description=Press L2 + Start for the Developer Options menu (the Font Viewer won't display anything; press /\ to exit), and R2 + Start for the Sample Viewer menu (no exit; reset console). Lower the
music before using the Sample Viewer.

Model Viewer Controls (not fully explained in-game):

Toggle Mode: Start
Next Actor: X
Prev Actor: O
Next Anim: Right
Prev Anim: Left
Add Clone: R1
Del Clone: L1
